# Web/JS/TS Development Rules

## Toolchain
- Runtime: bun
- Linter: biome
- Formatter: biome
- Type Checker: tsc

## Commands
- Install: `bun install`
- Lint: `bunx biome check .`
- Format: `bunx biome format --write .`
- Type Check: `bunx tsc --noEmit`

## Lockfile
- Prefer: `bun.lock` (text format)
- Legacy: `bun.lockb` (binary, accepted but not preferred)
